{
  "texts": [
    "This study also demonstrated the potential for multi-resolution models that interpolate between coarse-grained and atomistic simulations 79, 80.",
    "In parallel, Chao et al.",
    "presented a new approach to represent IDR ensembles and trained several different machine-learning architectures to predict global dimensions from sequence 81.",
    "Finally, Tesei and Trolle et al.",
    "recently performed an analogous assessment of the human IDR-ome using the CALVADOS2 force field 23, 28, 29."
  ]
}